    .guide
      .box
        h4 🍪 What Are Cookies?
        p Cookies are small files that store info about your visit to help improve your experience.

      .box
        h4 🧁 Why We Use Them
        p To remember preferences, enable logins, and improve website analytics.

      .box
        h4 🔍 Types of Cookies
        p We use essential, performance, and analytics cookies — no invasive tracking.

      .box
        h4 ❌ Opt-Out
        p You can disable cookies in your browser, but it may affect how Qastra works.

      .box
        h4 🔄 Policy Updates
        p We may change our cookie usage. Updates will be reflected here.

